1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,400
Without communication, you will not get anywhere.

2
00:00:03,400 --> 00:00:08,200
Your goal is to keep the correct buttons pressed for 3 seconds.

3
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:11,400
To do this, you will only use the terminals.

4
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:15,000
Many balls of different colors will appear on screen.

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:18,200
Each ball represents a button of that same color.

6
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:21,800
You must organize quickly and coordinate as a team.

7
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:24,800
When all the correct colors are pressed,

8
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,800
the countdown will begin.

9
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,600
If someone fails or lets go too early,

10
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,400
you will have to start again.

11
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:34,400
Think fast, coordinate positions,

12
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:36,400
and hold together.
